customValues.infoDesc:
After boyfriend roams around the grave room and shed, he discovers an enterance into a room known as the "QUITTER'S ROOM". After looking around for a bit, he notices a reflection of himself in the middle of the room. While looking at the reflection, he notices that his head is different in the reflection, replaced by a white face that was smiling. Something was mimicking and syncing his every move.


Based on Petscop 2 by Tony Domenico
